description: Austin Wilde is a pretty straight up guy. He knows what he wants, and when he wants it, he has no problem saying so. Adam Wirthmore is a student who passes his free time online in several chat rooms. And it seems as though Austin has taken an interest. So when he calls Adam one afternoon, he's got only one thing on his mind. Luckily for Austin, Adam is down with the program and free for the afternoon. A short bike ride later and the both of them will get what they really want.Enjoy!
title: Da Booty Call
